Changed contracts initialization mechanics into a main contract centered model.

Added submitting task solutions, voting on solutions, task reward caps, adding oneself as freelancer.
Finished submitting and voting on task solutions.
Implemented delayed withdrawls for security, changed removals to invalidations.

Debugged Main and Vault contracts so that they compile.
Used npm to install web3 instead of meteor. Minor changes to git-ipfs.coffee.

Fixed Dao.init() by changing how votableGroups is stored for VotingTypes.

Added auto directory creation for creating/cloning Git repos
Added comments. Changed promise structure of git-ipfs.coffee.
